PageTitle: display port high-precision rate detection result
FuncDef: The display port high-precision rate detection result command displays the high-precision rate detection result of an interface. The display port high-precision rate detection result command displays the high-precision rate detection result of an interface.
CLIs: display port high-precision rate detection result
Examples: <HUAWEI> display port high-precision rate detection result
ExtraInfo: After the port high-precision rate detection of a port is enabled, you can run this command to query the result of the high-precision rate detection of the port.
